        <h1 style="font-size:1.75rem; font-weight:800; color:#1e293b; margin-top:0.25rem;">Patient Hygiene &amp; Personal Care</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="color:#64748b; line-height:1.6;">Oral care, tympanic temperature, back rub, nocturia, and sleep promotion strategies.</p>
    <div style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
      <a href={`${base}/private/d439/hygiene-personal-care-slides`} style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.4rem; padding:0.45rem 1rem; background:#6366f1; color:#fff; border-radius:9999px; font-size:0.82rem; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;">▶ View as Slides</a>
