    <p style="font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em; color:#64748b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Contents</p>
    <ol style="margin:0; padding-left:1.25rem; color:#6366f1; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:2;">
      <li><a href="#oral-unconscious" style="color:#6366f1;">Oral Care for an Unconscious Patient</a></li>
      <li><a href="#oral-hygiene" style="color:#6366f1;">Oral Hygiene for an Unconscious Patient (Skills)</a></li>
      <li><a href="#tympanic" style="color:#6366f1;">Tympanic Temperature – Skills</a></li>
      <li><a href="#back-rub" style="color:#6366f1;">Back Rub – How and Why</a></li>
      <li><a href="#nocturia" style="color:#6366f1;">Nocturia – Definition &amp; Interventions</a></li>
      <li><a href="#sleep" style="color:#6366f1;">Alternative Sleep Suggestions / Promote Sleep</a></li>
      <li><a href="#sleep-apnea" style="color:#6366f1;">Sleep Apnea</a></li>
    </ol>
